The '''A35''' is a {{convert|296|km|mi|adj=mid|-long}} road linking [[Namibia]] to [[Sehithwa]] and then onto the [[A3 road (Botswana)|A3 road]] to access [[Francistown]]. The route is notable for the amount of airports on the road.
