'''Itsandra''' was one of the two major sultanates on the island of [[Grand Comore]] before the [[France|French]] colonization of the [[Comoros]]. It was taken over by the [[Sultanate of Bambao]] in 1886 and became a part of the united Sultanate of [[Ngazidja]].
